  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">TRANSFORM LIVES OF 3000 DRUG USERS IN KIBERA SLUMS</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will continue providing comprehensive HIV services to people who use and inject drugs. The focus will include community outreach to identify the victims and link them to the clinics for provision of comprehensive services such as HIV testing, TB and  STI screening and treatment, condom distribution and extensive psycho-social  counselling including risk reduction counselling. This approach will be in line with the national policies and Kenya AIDS Strategic Framework IV.</narrative>
  </description>
